 have set an ambitious goal to ourselves - to create the fusion of already successful real estate agency and a new generation of tour agency.\r\nAt the same time we focus on every detail of not solely Asia region but consider the latest trends of the tourism industry in general as well.\r\n\r\nWith the merits of our experienced team and the use of advanced IT technologies we guarantee service complying with European quality standards and, of course, the needs and mentality of CIS countries (where most of our staff members come from).\r\nThe current situation inside former CIS countries (and worldwide) contributes to the fact that people with different income are increasingly taking thought if not to change the residence place for good but to live the snowbird season or take more long journeys to Asia at least. This also entails the continuous development of IT infrastructure in the region and still less obstacles to remote work and development of local business projects.\r\n\r\nTherefore our group decided to build its headquarters in Phuket which is not only the largest and the most developed island of the Kingdom of Thailand but also in the top 100 of the best resorts in the world.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="0"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Our benefits</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][text_with_icons style="style_two" columns="three_columns"][text_with_icon icon_type="fontawesome_icon" font_awesome_icon="heart" title="Individual approach" text="We consider individually every request and select the best solutions to everyone who addressed us. Also, unlike other companies we offer ..." read_more_text="Читать далее" read_more_link="http://starasiap.temp.swtest.ru/en/about-us/individual-approach/"][text_with_icon icon_type="fontawesome_icon" font_awesome_icon="map-marker" title="Extensive property database" text="Our company permanently collaborates with a large number of villas, apartments, hotels and clubs in different regions of the island. This ..." read_more_text="Читать далее" read_more_link=" http://starasia.phuketeasy.com/en/about-us/database/"][text_with_icon icon_type="fontawesome_icon" font_awesome_icon="usd" title="Reasonable prices" text="We offer the most favorable prices on each of our services. Thanks to our long-term and successful cooperation with the property owners we ..." read_more_text="Читать далее" read_more_link="http://starasia.phuketeasy.com/en/about-us/price/"][/text_with_icons][text_with_icons style="style_two" columns="three_columns"][text_with_icon icon_type="fontawesome_icon" font_awesome_icon="lock" title="Security issues" text="The company is officially registered in Thailand (Tax ID: 0835559005706). We sign the agreement on providing service for you to be best sure ..." read_more_text="Читать далее" read_more_link="http://starasia.phuketeasy.com/en/about-us/security/"][text_with_icon icon_type="fontawesome_icon" font_awesome_icon="refresh" title="Тур-Сервис 360°" text="Мы не являемся привычным тур-агентством,так как мы не навязываем Вам пакетные туры, когда приехав на 10 дней и вылезаете из отеля лишь .." read_more_text="Читать далее" read_more_link="#"][/text_with_icons][vc_empty_space height="32"][/vc_column][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1466460673943{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="32"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][:]', '[:ru]О нас[:en]About us[:]', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2017-01-05 12:44:42', '2017-01-05 09:44:42', '', 0, 'http://houzez07.favethemes.com/?page_id=1776', 0, 'page', '', 0),
